#: ../../release_notes.rst:50
msgid ""
"Add the following Clifford gates, that already exist in the circuit "
"library, to the :class:`.Clifford` class: :class:`.SXGate`, "
":class:`.SXdgGate`, :class:`.CYGate`, :class:`.DCXGate`, "
":class:`.iSwapGate` and :class:`.ECRGate`."
