msgid ""
"Fixed a bug in the NumPy-based eigensolvers "
"(:class:`~.minimum_eigensolvers.NumPyMinimumEigensolver` / "
":class:`~.eigensolvers.NumPyEigensolver`) and in the SciPy-based time "
"evolvers (:class:`.SciPyRealEvolver` / :class:`.SciPyImaginaryEvolver`), "
"where operators that support conversion to sparse matrices, such as "
